{"tid":743152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指回歸前施政較易　張炳良：麥理浩大規模起公屋，今天做不到","createTime":"2018-07-15T07:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T08:19:01.000Z","uid":39521,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fc36e0edae7701ad14bbefbdd313b4dd43c1da79","tid":743152,"uid":39521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180715/s00001/1531623664830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180715%2Fs00001%2F1531623664830&d=A7PZhSMhbKKmWPPLr8B8djQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=7ce41f56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180715%2Fs00001%2F1531623664830&h=9c493fd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180715/s00001/1531623664830</a><br />\n<br />\n土地供應專責小組4月起展開為期5個月的「大辯論」，就18個土地供應選項諮詢公眾，近日已有包括特首林鄭月娥在內的多名政府官員，率先表示填海是無可避免。前運輸及房屋局長張炳良接受商台訪問時，就表示土地供應選項應是多管齊下，以應付短中長期目標。他又直言回歸前政府較易推動政策，指如赤鱲角機場、前港督麥理浩大規模起公屋等基建，如以今天標準的話將不能做到。<br />\n<br />\n張炳良指，社會在房屋問題上需要有決心解決，但他覺得因社會上有不少小眾聲音，諮詢時都各陳己見，因此對社會在「大辯論」後能凝聚共識不敢樂觀。不過，他相信土地供應專責小組可讓社會聚焦議題，但此後仍要依賴政府積極推動。<br />\n<br />\n被問及回歸前政府是否較易推動政策，張炳良同意此說，指原因其一是回歸前由於政治、政制等因素，社會沒有那麽分化；至於其二則是規劃、環評等程序不同所致。他舉例如赤鱲角機場、前港督麥理浩大規模起公屋等基建，若依照今天的地區諮詢、城規標準等程序，將不能落成，直言社會須有取捨，不要留給下一代包袱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/153902_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F153902_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=aa026690&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f6d2efd2656528ce3d1fc1a298a72d057a1e9fe","tid":743152,"uid":64345,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"係度講風涼話"},{"pid":"652751f2924fe00ace661c739d28eb7bb85cf95c","tid":743152,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"香港人如果個個安居樂業<br />\n樓價會大跌 損害地產商利益<br />\n政府唔會咁做"},{"pid":"23bf1635dcf8cad6afab6c4cf33d0574adbac20a","tid":743152,"uid":180156,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"其實點解唔比填海"},{"pid":"e499f5ea68dc9fdaa7da819d4e78abab975d7212","tid":743152,"uid":191647,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b833e127d278ec6e10b958102527032082a2a34","tid":743152,"uid":98163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"暗示現時政府唔夠權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9acde05509b057d8f3abcf815c80635ced5267","tid":743152,"uid":38671,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"英國人由零開始建設香港唔難?<br />\n廢就廢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27dd8664d91d00d42f59f44290794fd55dc4ad2","tid":743152,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b833e127d278ec6e10b958102527032082a2a34","tid":743152,"uid":98163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"暗示現時政府唔夠權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:53:06.000Z","msg":"係害怕權勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9883670fbaee896dd785592e06738e6ce47efdd","tid":743152,"uid":37730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:54:08.000Z","msg":"中肯d佢又無講錯"},{"pid":"839c0fc76dfc69e4ef72267118671187670e3c70","tid":743152,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9883670fbaee896dd785592e06738e6ce47efdd","tid":743152,"uid":37730,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:54:08.000Z","msg":"中肯d佢又無講錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"個陣無人講環保同保育係事實，反正d 地係英王<img src=\"/assets/faces